{
  "stem": "10587.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I go-- and they said to me-- in the line, says-- when I got in the line, the guy's standing there and say, remember, when he asks you [SPEAKING GERMAN], tell him, [SPEAKING GERMAN]-- metalworks.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because the rumor had it that this transport is going to the Krupps factory, to Funfteichen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "At that time, we didn't know-- we didn't know the name of Funfteichen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But that's what really happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I got back, and this young man, this Sturmfuhrer says, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I turned around, and he said, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he sent me to the right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's how I got out of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went to Funfteichen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I want to ask you a couple things about Auschwitz, OK?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Since that's what we're talking about, before you get to the Krupps factory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "First, I know that you said that you knew that people died in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When you were-- but how did you really-- did you know they were-- when did you know that people were gassed and about the crematoriums?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All this I have learned from my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before coming to Auschwitz-- right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was always the-- the smell of-- like burnt rubber.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I realized after a while, you know, that-- and everybody else was talking about it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The crematoriums have been fired up again-- in other words, because they were-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in Auschwitz, they were going to day and night, the crematoriums.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there was a constant smell.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
